Package fr.upmc.dtgui.gui

Interface Summary
ActuatorDataSenderInterface The interface ActuatorDataSenderInterface provides a common supertype for all actuator data sender threads used by teleoperation stations to send commands to robots.
RobotTeleoperationBoard The interface RobotTeleoperationBoard defines the minimal set of functionalities of robot teleoperation boards expected by the hosting teleoperation stations.
SensorDataReceptorInterface The interface SensorDataReceptorInterface defines a common supertype for all sensor data receptor threads used by teleoperation stations to receive the sensory data from robots.
 

Class Summary
PersonalizedGUI  
PositionDisplay The class PositionDisplay implements a radar-like display for the robot teleoperation GUI.
RobotSelector The class RobotSelector defines a panel to gather buttons used to select the robot that will be currently under the control of the teleoperation station.
TeleoperationGUI The class TeleoperationGUI is a JFrame representing the overall graphical user interface of a control station for robots.
